name: Red Aventurine Necklace
description: This necklace is made of three strands of red aventurine (natural) and glass.  Warm burgundy shades grace nine strands of merlot-colored wire twisted into three groups of floating translucent glass beads, lustrous glass pearls and subtle red aventurine chips.  The lightweight necklace playfully drapes at 18 inches, with a two-inch extender chain and steel lobster claw clasp.

name: Mussel Shell Necklace
description: This necklace is constructed of mussel shells (dyed) in shades of blue and green.  The shell coins measure 15mm.  Vibrant and shimmering with color, the mussel shells and imitation rhodium bead necklace, with three strands of white cotton cord and an imitation rhodium lobster claw clasp, is approximately 18 inches long and includes a 2-inch extender chain.

name: Acrylic Crystals, Seed Beads & Fringed Beaded Donut Necklace
description: This necklace is made of acrylic crystals and seed beads with a monofilament fringe.  A beaded 30mm donut with 1-1/2 inch double-strand accent is used as a focal piece.  The fringed beads are secured with metallic crimp beads.  The necklace is 16 inches long, and the steel lobster claw clasp and 2-inch extender chain are in an antiqued gunmetal finish.

name: Gold, Orange & Tan Beads & Seed Beads Necklace
description: This necklace has many strands of glass and acrylic beads.  It is fashion jewelry with a vintage-inspired elegance.  Antiqued gold color chain and many various components join multiple strands of tiny orange and tan beads.  The style's in the details with strands of iridescent seed beads adding a luminous shine, roped open-circle links and intricately patterned gold-colored saucer beads.  The necklace is about 30 inches long and secured with a lobster claw clasp.

name: Red Agate Stones & Chips Freeform Focal Necklace
description: This multi-strand necklace, made of red agate (dyed/heated) stones and chips, is 28 inches long.  The attention-getting red agate freeform focal piece is individually cut to enhance the natural pattern of the stone.  The brown nylon macrame cord is accented with red agate chips and is adjustable.
